{"tid":2307134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"律師警署內被黑警粗口辱罵、挑釁打架、威脅拘捕","createTime":"2020-12-01T03:35:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T05:04:31.000Z","uid":321059,"like":40,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"f907cf2347264d3f3d73003feba01b4be453b4e2","tid":2307134,"uid":321059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T03:35:27.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">巴裔律師投訴警署內遭粗暴對待 無委任證便衣警粗口辱罵、挑釁打架、威脅拘捕<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n（獨媒報導）警署爆出粗暴對待律師的事件。一名巴基斯坦裔律師向《獨媒》表示，上週二（11月24日）在尖沙咀警署協助被捕人士後，<span class=\"red\">突遭一名身穿便服、身上無委任證、相信屬刑事偵緝處（CID）的男警以粗口辱罵，其後近8名警員圍住他挑釁打架，又威脅可用任何罪名將他拘捕，</span>直至他指出現場有目擊者才被帶離現場。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\nC繼續與翻譯員談話，<span class=\"red\">惟5秒後男警突然走向他並大罵：「律師，屌你老母！」</span>C形容，當時極為錯愕和憤怒，立即回罵男警。他一度問翻譯員自己做了什麼、警員為何有此反應，但翻譯員僅表示自己為警察工作，不能幫忙。<span class=\"red\">期間有警員嘗試協助該男警冷靜，也有另一女警以粗口辱罵他，並要求他離開</span>，但C拒絕，直指需要知道該名警員的身分以作投訴。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\nC續指，該男警拒絕表露身分，後來相信屬同一小隊、身穿便服的7至8名警員圍住他，<span class=\"red\">有人擺出要打架的姿勢不斷挑釁及作身體碰撞，有人以手踭撞他的背，及有一名個子矮小、非常年輕近乎「孩子」的男警不斷以C聽不明白的英語辱罵他。</span><br />\n<br />\nC隨即向警員指出，現場仍有另一名印度裔的女翻譯員目睹過程。他形容，那刻警察才突然意識到有目擊者，遂立即將他帶離現場。其時有3名警員大力抓住他搭𨋢，C形容，<span class=\"red\">警員全都很「聰明」，不停假裝他嘗試掙脫逃走，但是C全程舉高雙手站在原地：「我是律師，我不是罪犯，為何這樣對我？」</span><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1079237?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1079237%3F&d=3wrM%2FJom4zLweqSprMIx0nljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=c6ea646e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1079237%3F&h=08df5a6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1079237?</a>"},{"pid":"2868b257286b87cc4fcb30dacf6927cfdc29da5c","tid":2307134,"uid":309148,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T03:42:08.000Z","msg":"因為律師都是罪犯<br />\n犯咩罪？<br />\n莫須有罪<br />\n<br />\n任何一個人只要唔做狗 就係罪人<br />\n做狗就唔係罪人 因為人狗有別"},{"pid":"deae18c95ed4b4346236d2cdcf3ae4fbbb481090","tid":2307134,"uid":49329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T03:49:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ad0391250743c5a5b40825262779955a5d2ff24","tid":2307134,"uid":9116,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T03:50:39.000Z","msg":"讀書少見人讀書多咪嬲咪妒嫉囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d87f81352e28cea7d8a533de0a40715e6eaac0b8","tid":2307134,"uid":9116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ad0391250743c5a5b40825262779955a5d2ff24","tid":2307134,"uid":9116,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T03:50:39.000Z","msg":"讀書少見人讀書多咪嬲咪妒嫉囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T03:52:20.000Z","msg":"妒忌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f844eb9f4f27acfda5ab207aeb812d0e78603886","tid":2307134,"uid":2383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T03:55:39.000Z","msg":"Bobo 黑社會唔係假<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"084dbf08fb7aadaf752475fb6f79744558885ddf","tid":2307134,"uid":139294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T03:56:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"61640779447036225a008c8edca17887a26e2531","tid":2307134,"uid":159414,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T03:56:52.000Z","msg":"有一名個子矮小、非常年輕近乎「孩子」的男警不斷以C聽不明白的英語辱罵他<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嘲笑意味很濃<br />\n狗狗又要嬲嬲豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好心唔好用埋啲人聽唔明嘅英文啦<br />\n講返狗話咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人哋話矮仔多計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢隻狗應該例外<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啲毅進仔一見人哋讀得多書<br />\n唔使做狗就心生恨意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔使出聲都自知不如<br />\n吠返幾聲拎存在感"},{"pid":"652a43ce2184b5d36a8e66ea8b62566dec51a9ff","tid":2307134,"uid":296600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T03:57:49.000Z","msg":"呢啲就冇人推"},{"pid":"0e73566a1f88b7e3ca21472547e0abea97c4a374","tid":2307134,"uid":73340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T04:02:32.000Z","msg":"誰大誰惡誰正確"},{"pid":"791c19e6a3ac14c92a0a258172a9c5d85dd472ef","tid":2307134,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T04:08:10.000Z","msg":"點解要搞個律師？唔明？！"},{"pid":"38164be9bd3a23cc432a4ed5205c1d2b44c8e8ff","tid":2307134,"uid":123053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T04:15:29.000Z","msg":"律師都咁樣<br />\n被拉嗰啲實打到仆街"},{"pid":"81eb70455273005bb0ed61c5399e475e93c0fd78","tid":2307134,"uid":15730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T04:19:23.000Z","msg":"死黑警high撚左野"},{"pid":"fb24cd97cc0897336d729eee258627337f282ab1","tid":2307134,"uid":345459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T04:23:17.000Z","msg":"偽進仔就係毅進仔"},{"pid":"edde31fcf2143638d671d3bd5c4f818891b9f8f4","tid":2307134,"uid":112457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T04:24:30.000Z","msg":"呢D都係新聞? 係人到知警察係咩人啦"},{"pid":"3d335a804a0624648bf942b78d04a9668073d32d","tid":2307134,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T04:25:25.000Z","msg":"邊個同你講便衣係警署入面就係警察<br />\n可以係黑社會<br />\n圍住你嗰班全部都可以係黑社會<br />\n<br />\n警察不嬲都要8個字之後先到場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgm